+ BROADCAST +
Broadcasts a message to every player.
Action type: Broadcast

Usage: BROADCAST <DURATION> <MESSAGE>

Arguments:
<duration>
  Required: YES
  Type: Float (Number)
  The duration of the message. Variables are supported.

<message>
  Required: YES
  Type: String (Message/Text)
  The message. Variables are supported.
